Adding all four categories, we have  \[(10-x)+x+(15-x) + 8 = 30.\]Simplifying gives $33-x = 30$, so $x = \boxed{3}$.

The focus of the parabola $y^2 = 4ax$ is $F = (a,0),$ and the directrix is $x = -a.$  Then
\[PQ = PF + QF.\][asy]
unitsize(0.8 cm);

